<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Collision Course Studios - We make arcade racing games for everyone</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../Styles/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../Styles/mobile.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../Styles/games.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Oswald:wght@200..700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="../Scripts/menu.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="oswald-header">
        <a href="../home/"><img src="../Images/Logo_Final.png" alt="Collision Course Studios Logo" class="logo"></a>
        <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Toggle menu">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </button>
        <nav id="nav">
            <ul class="right">
                <li><a href="../home/">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#games">Games</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="../contact/">Contact</a></li>
                <!--<li><a href="#discord"><img src="../Images/Discord_Logo.png" alt="Discord Logo" class="socials"></a></li>-->
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="homepage">
        <section id="home">
            <!--<img src="../Images/Logo_Final.png" alt="Collision Course Studios Logo" class="home-logo">-->
            <div class="home-title">
                <h1>Collision Course Studios</h1>
                <h3>Off to reinvent the racing fantasy</h3>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!--<section id="games">
            <iframe src="../games/gamelist.html" title="Our Games" class="game-list"></iframe>
        </section>-->

        <section id="games">

            <div id="banner">
                <div class="banner-inner">
                    <h2>Our Games<!--<span class="banner-flag">🏁</span>--></h2>
                    <!--<p>Arcade racing built for everyone. Pick up, play, and chase that high score.</p>-->
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2>Collision Course Games</h2>

            <div class="game-grid">

                <div class="game-card">
                    <div class="game-card-thumb">
                         <img src="../Images/FuelFrenzy_Thumbnail.png" alt="Fuel Frenzy Thumbnail">
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-body">
                        <h3 class="game-card-title">Fuel Frenzy</h3>
                        <p class="game-card-desc">
                            A track racing game where the objective is to collect fuel
                            and reach the highest score possible. How long can you keep
                            the tank topped up?
                        </p>
                        <div class="game-card-tags">
                            <span class="game-tag">Arcade</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Racing</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">High Score</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-footer">
                        <a class="play-btn" href="https://www.crazygames.com/game/fuel-frenzy-ahk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Play Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="game-card">
                    <div class="game-card-thumb">
                         <img src="../Images/SpaceCadetMinesweeper_Thumbnail.png" alt="Space Cadet Minesweeper Thumbnail">
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-body">
                        <h3 class="game-card-title">Space Cadet Minesweeper</h3>
                        <p class="game-card-desc">
                            A space mining game where you and 2 friends scan asteroids and coordinate a ship to mine valuable resources
                            whilst avoiding the mines within. Communication and teamwork are key to success!
                        </p>
                        <div class="game-card-tags">
                            <span class="game-tag">Arcade</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Online co-op</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">3 Players</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-footer">
                        <a class="play-btn" href="https://mm-13.itch.io/spacecadetminesweeper" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Play Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="game-card">
                    <div class="game-card-thumb no-image">
                         <!--<img src="../Images/SpaceCadetMinesweeper_Thumbnail.png" alt="Space Cadet Minesweeper Thumbnail">-->
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-body">
                        <h3 class="game-card-title">Build That Car! - Upcoming</h3>
                        <p class="game-card-desc">
                            Built the car you've always dreamed of, and take it for a spin in our arcade racing playground!
                        </p>
                        <div class="game-card-tags">
                            <span class="game-tag">Arcade</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Car</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Modding</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-footer">
                        <a class="play-btn" href="" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Play Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="games-subblock">
            <h2>Games by Founders</h2>

            <div class="game-grid">

                <div class="game-card">
                    <div class="game-card-thumb">
                         <img src="../Images/HuntsmanIsle_Thumbnail.png" alt="Huntsman Isle Thumbnail">
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-body">
                        <h3 class="game-card-title">Huntsman Isle</h3>
                        <p class="game-card-desc">
                            Scavenge for parts, avoid traps and sneak through the unknown land of Huntsman Isle to rebuild your escape... or fall prey to the island's relentless hunter.
                        </p>
                        <div class="game-card-tags">
                            <span class="game-tag">Horror</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Exploration</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Survival</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-footer">
                        <a class="play-btn" href="https://mm-13.itch.io/huntsman-isle" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get On Itch</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="game-card">
                    <div class="game-card-thumb">
                         <img src="../Images/SouperBloody_Thumbnail.png" alt="Souper Bloody Thumbnail">
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-body">
                        <h3 class="game-card-title">Souper Bloody</h3>
                        <p class="game-card-desc">
                            Souper Bloody is a rougelite hack-and-slash where you play as a demon from the lowest layer of the Underlasagne. You can only move around in the blood of your enemies, so get slashing!
                        </p>
                        <div class="game-card-tags">
                            <span class="game-tag">Action</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Roguelike</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Hack and SLash</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-footer">
                        <a class="play-btn" href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/4368980/Souper_Bloody/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Get On Steam</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="game-card">
                    <div class="game-card-thumb no-image">
                         <!--<img src="../Images/SpaceCadetMinesweeper_Thumbnail.png" alt="Space Cadet Minesweeper Thumbnail">-->
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-body">
                        <h3 class="game-card-title">Man's Best Friend</h3>
                        <p class="game-card-desc">
                            A game where you play as a dog...
                        </p>
                        <div class="game-card-tags">
                            <span class="game-tag">Horror</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Single-player</span>
                            <span class="game-tag">Psychological</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="game-card-footer">
                        <a class="play-btn" href="https://mathiesvdb.itch.io/mans-best-friend" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Play Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        </section>

        <section id="about">
            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p>Collision Course Studios was founded by a team of four students, studying Independent Game Production at Howest - Digital Arts & Entertainment.<br>
                Whilst doing their internship at Flanders Game Hub, they choose to start a game studio together with a focus on creating amazing racing experiences.</p>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Collision Course Studios. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>